{{Infobox settlement |official_name =Hashjin |native_name =هشجين |settlement_type = City |pushpin_map =Iran |mapsize =150px |subdivision_type = [[List of countries|Country]] |subdivision_name = {{flag|Iran}} |subdivision_type1 =[[Provinces of Iran|Province]] |subdivision_name1 =[[Ardabil Province|Ardabil]] |subdivision_type2 =[[Counties of Iran|County]] |subdivision_name2 =[[Khalkhal County|Khalkhal]] |subdivision_type3 =[[Bakhsh]] |subdivision_name3 =[[Khvoresh Rostam District|Khvoresh Rostam]] |leader_title = |leader_name = |established_title = |established_date = |area_total_km2 = |area_footnotes = |population_as_of = 2016 Census |population_total =5,725 <ref>https://www.amar.org.ir/english</ref> |population_density_km2 =auto |timezone = [[Iran Standard Time|IRST]] |utc_offset = +3:30 |timezone_DST = [[Iran Daylight Time|IRDT]] |utc_offset_DST = +4:30 |coordinates = {{coord|37|21|35|N|48|18|58|E|region:IR|display=inline,title}} |elevation_m = |area_code = |website = |footnotes ={{GEOnet2|32FA880A2C793774E0440003BA962ED3}} }} '''Hashjin'''({{lang-fa|هشجين}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''Hashjin'''; also known as '''Heshajeyn''', '''Heshajīn''', '''Heshīīn''', '''Hīshen''', '''Shain''', and '''Shein''')<ref>{{GEOnet3|-3066483}}</ref> is a city in and the capital of the [[Khvoresh Rostam District]], in [[Khalkhal County]], [[Ardabil Province]], [[Iran]].
It is located east of the [[Qizil Üzan]] river, in the [[Alborz|Alborz (''Elburz'') mountain range]]
At the 2006 census, its population was 4,518, in 1,199 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|24}}</ref>
